defaultStringSubscript

public static GlobalsNodeSubscript defaultStringSubscript
This static class provides a default class that uses the default string for the subscript. Note we don't actually want numerous instances of this class. In fact, it needs to be an invariant that each GlGraph has only one subscript instance.
